data.description: This enchanting home is located in the heart of Twin Falls. Nestled in a quiet neighborhood in between Thomsen Park & O’Leary Middle School, this location provides plenty of opportunities for outings within walking distance. This home was renovated in 2022. You'll find newer carpet & LVP flooring throughout the entire home, a new roof, new gutters, and newer light fixtures. This home offers an open concept living room and kitchen that is truly the heart of the home, vaulted ceilings, the master sits at the rear of the home with an on-suite master bath and a large master walk-in closet, a generous backyard that is fenced with a fully automatic sprinkler system, a storage shed, a large dog run, a dedicated gardening space, a built-in work bench in the garage, a ceiling mount heater in the garage to keep you warm while working on your hobbies, along with RV parking for your toys and your convenience. NO HOA fees! VA Assumable Loan for qualified Veteran! Great rate!
